domain:bus:dev = 0000:14:00
[21833.389103] TW686x 0000:14:00.0: removing
[21833.416557] TW686x 0000:14:00.0: removed
[..]

I have no idea why the link goes down (hardware issue?),
but it's better to handle it gracefully :)

